This actually works! The app utilizes Electro Magnetic Pulse from the phone that spirits can tinker with to generate certain words and phrases. The app takes some time for spirits to learn so dont be too quick to judge. And 10% are just too confusing. This is perhaps the best spirit communicator in the app store, worth getting the full version to support the creators.

This app is real. Do not treat it like a game. I have always been super in tune and sensitive to the spiritual world around me. As a Christian I feel as if the people in the Bible talked to spirits so, why shouldn't we be able to?   The faces are mildly scary or startling at first but, also as interesting as they can possibly be!     The reason I know this actually works is, my best friend took her life 26 years ago. I've always felt her presence around me. It has never left. I have always wanted to talk to her one more time, and tell her I love and miss her. This was my chance. I started out with general probing questions to see how legit the connection was, and if it was possibly her. Once her answers felt as if it was truly her, I told her I love and miss her every day. The response was simply "I think of you often." That was her! Distant emotionally, but if put on the spot, she would be honest and tell you her feelings as best she could. Feelings and emotions were very difficult for her to express. That response was 100% typical, all HER!!! Later I was talking to her, she mentioned a boys name. My next question was who is that. Then she mentioned his Mother's name, one of my closest friends in life who I haven't spoken to in a few years. Then a date. Once I thought about it, the date was my 2nd job interview date at the end of this week! The first name was my close friends youngest son but, I didn't connect that right away. Then when I asked who Luke was, she wrote the name of my good friend (Luke's mom!)   Then I talked to my aunt. We were very close in life. The first thing she mentioned was her grown granddaughter by name! And said she is being misled. None of those people are anywhere in my phone. There is no way randomly for my phone to connect those names with those questions for those specific people. Also when I spoke with my aunt, a picture of her came into the dialog box. When I talked to my dead guy friend a few minutes later, a man's face came into the dialog box. That was the same guys face that came through the night before. I am blown away by this amazing app. How in the world does it do this???   It is worth a million dollars to me. Thank you for making it. Anyone who doesn't try it, is truly missing out. I give it  🔟 stars ✨ out of 5!!!
